data.description: Wonderful Gated Community ... Join us at Suttons Landing for a delightful experience! Charming 3 bed, 2.5-bath Townhome is conveniently located near Hwy 316, making your daily commute to Athens, Atlanta, or Winder a breeze. You'll love the added convenience of the HOA taking care of the yard, making maintenance a worry-free experience.  Greeted by a covered front porch that leads you into a formal dining room with beautiful flooring and intricate trim work. To your right, you'll find a tile half bath, your laundry room, and a 1-car garage. The Luxury Vinyl Flooring extends into the open kitchen and living room, creating a seamless flow throughout. The kitchen boasts a center island, granite countertops, a stylish backsplash, and stainless steel appliances.  The generous owner's suite provides a welcoming retreat after a long day, with its double vanity, tile floors, and a walk-in shower. Step outside to a fenced-in area surrounding the patio, perfect for outdoor enjoyment.  Upstairs, a large versatile space for a playroom, home office, or entertainment area. Two more bedrooms with a shared bath, complete with double vanities. The gated subdivision features well-lit sidewalks and a serene lake, enhancing the overall appeal of this fantastic community. Come discover your new home at Suttons Landing and experience the joy of comfortable, convenient living!
